addition.32: * Marks a "top-level" type-variable usage as (a) a Kotlin platform type when the type argument is

addition.34: * to "non-nullable when non-nullable; nullable when nullable" (like the Android <a
addition.36: * NullFromTypeParam}). We use this to "undo" {@link ElementTypesAreNonnullByDefault}.
